snippet.title: You Will Die Here Tonight - Launch Trailer - Indie Survival Horror
snippet.description:
Out Now!!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1446350/You_Will_Die_Here_Tonight/

You will die here tonight -- but what you leave behind is up to you.

Enter Breckenridge Estate as Aries Division, and elite squad in search of a savage killer, and face the horrors of their past as six characters explore the estate from different angles.

As each team member dies a grisly death, you will leave behind consequences, puzzle progress, and resources for the survivors.

Die well. Survive. Escape...?
Discord: https://discord.gg/swY8HMjW
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpiralBound_Dev
Website: https://www.youwilldieheretonight.com/
